	(text "5V USB Bus -> Diode ->5V bus\nNominally USB at 5.25 or lower won't pass unless\nno 12 V present.\n12V -> 5V Regulator is \npulled up to always enable in either 12 or usb connected\nThis means if no 12V present enters LV protection\nDoes not pull 5V low so 5VUSB will dominate."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 20.574 119.38 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
